A '''carbine''' was a category of ranged weapons generally smaller than [[Rifle/Legends|rifles]] but larger than [[Pistol/Legends|pistols]]. The distinction between pistol, carbine and rifle existed for most types of ranged weapons, including [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] ([[Blaster carbine/Legends|blaster carbine]]), [[Disruptor/Legends|disruptor]] ([[Disruptor rifle/Legends|disruptor carbine]]) and [[Slugthrower/Legends|slugthrower]] ([[slugthrower carbine]]).<ref name="SWG">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>

Although carbines and rifles could often look very similar, these two categories of weapons usually had distinct characteristics. The rifles could generally fire at greater range while carbines had faster firing rate.<ref name="SWG" />

